title: [Arctic Tundra, High Plain]
description: A sparkling peninsula of ice bridges the deep ravine in front of the garrison entrance.  High overhead, a lone falcon calls out as it passes, searching for prey.  Tiny tracks in the snow give evidence that there is more to this tundra than meets the eye.

A moonlit peninsula of ice bridges the deep ravine in front of the garrison entrance.  High overhead, a lone snowy owl calls out as it passes, searching for prey.  Tiny tracks in the snow give evidence that there is more to this tundra than meets the eye.
